    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great? You\u2019ve found it! I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in wonderful shape and has been really well-loved, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. It\u2019s super comfy and runs smoothly\u2014perfect for those long weekend trips or just your daily commute. Come take it for a spin, I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have! \u2728",
      "price": 32500.0,
